The exploration mode is one of the options in the main gameplay page which is top of the middle screen's view on mobile
and also that "mobile phone's screen" is on the left side of the desktop's 1/3 screens perspective.

This mode contains 4 types of exploration modes which are:
- streets/fields exploration
- districts/lands exploration
- regions exploration
- continental exploration

1. Streets/fields exploration mode is a basic and precise view of certain places within small parts of cities "districts"
   or within the area of villages, forsts, plains, lake/sea coasts and hills that are outside of the urban area.

   













